{"id": 239767606, "title": "Tom Brady's Patriots Hall of Fame Ring Revealed in Behind-The-Scenes Ceremony Video", "text": "Tom Brady fans have even more content to consume. The New England Patriots released behind the scenes coverage from Brady's Patriots Hall of Fame induction ceremony. It offers a new perspective on the ceremony and allows viewers to experience the night in a different light. The video showcases the set up process for the event, as well as interviews, alternate angles and other content that was previously unavailable to viewers. Viewers also got a look at Brady's massive Patriots Hall of Fame ring, presented to him by team owner Robert Kraft and his former teammates Julian Edelman and Rob Gronkowski: The event took place June 12th and was a celebration of the legendary quarterback's 20-year tenure in New England. He led the team to six Super Bowl victories and a 219-64 regular season record. He earned three MVP awards during his time with the franchise. The event featured many guests, including former Patriots coach Bill Belichick and several of Brady's favorite targets like Rob Gronkowski, Julian Edelman and Randy Moss. Even Peyton Manning, Brady's long-time AFC rival, was in attendance. The new look at the event will give viewers a chance to relive and appreciate the effort put into the ceremony", "summary": "Tom Brady fans have even more content to consume. The New England Patriots released behind the scenes coverage from Brady's Patriots Hall of Fame induction\u2026", "url": "https://bleacherreport.com/articles/10125713-tom-bradys-patriots-hall-of-fame-ring-revealed-in-behind-the-scenes-ceremony-video", "image": "https://media.bleacherreport.com/image/upload/v1719095181/cq2mbdbmxrghgfccu3wb.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-23 01:55:24", "author": "Jack Murray", "authors": ["Jack Murray"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": 1.0}